<h3 id="custom-template"><a class="header-anchor" href="#custom-template" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Custom template</h3>
<p>You can customize HTML templates for options.</p>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;template&gt;\n  &lt;el-select v-model=\&quot;value6\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Select\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;el-option v-for=\&quot;item in cities\&quot; :key=\&quot;item.value\&quot; :label=\&quot;item.label\&quot; :value=\&quot;item.value\&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;span style=\&quot;float: left\&quot;&gt;{{ item.label }}&lt;/span&gt;\n      &lt;span style=\&quot;float: right; color: #8492a6; font-size: 13px\&quot;&gt;{{ item.value }}&lt;/span&gt;\n    &lt;/el-option&gt;\n  &lt;/el-select&gt;\n&lt;/template&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\n  export default {\n    data() {\n      return {\n        cities: [{\n          value: 'Beijing',\n          label: 'Beijing'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Shanghai',\n          label: 'Shanghai'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Nanjing',\n          label: 'Nanjing'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Chengdu',\n          label: 'Chengdu'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Shenzhen',\n          label: 'Shenzhen'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Guangzhou',\n          label: 'Guangzhou'\n        }],\n        value6: ''\n      }\n    }\n  }\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><template>
  <el-select v-model="value6" placeholder="Select">
    <el-option v-for="item in cities" :key="item.value" :label="item.label" :value="item.value">
      <span style="float: left">{{ item.label }}</span>
      <span style="float: right; color: #8492a6; font-size: 13px">{{ item.value }}</span>
    </el-option>
  </el-select>
</template>


</div>
                    <p>Insert customized HTML templates into the slot of <code>el-option</code>.</p>

                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">template</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-select</span> <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"value6"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Select"</span>&gt;</span>
    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-option</span>
      <span class="hljs-attr">v-for</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"item in cities"</span>
      <span class="hljs-attr">:key</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"item.value"</span>
