  </el-select>
</template>


</div>
                    <p>Use <code>el-option-group</code> to group the options, and its <code>label</code> attribute stands for the name of the group.</p>

                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">template</span>&gt;</span>
